"statistic value of 10.72, with 2 d.f. and *p*-value = 0.005."
msgstr ""

#: ../../Ch10/Ch10_ChiSquare_2.rst:256
msgid ""
"That was easy, wasn’t it! You can also ask jamovi to show you the expected "
